"Koyaushe saka Grylli a bayan wakili mai bada amsa (e.g. Caddy, Nginx, ko "
"Traefik) kuma raba shi ta hanyar HTTPS. Dole ne bayanan masu amfani masu "
"mahimmanci su zama an ɓoye yayin tafiya."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:50
msgid ""
"Ensure the data folder (database) is backed up regularly. Backups are stored"
" in the 'backups' folder."
msgstr ""
"Tabbatar cewa folda ɗin bayanai (database) an yi ajiyar baƙin ciki a kan mai"
" masaukinka"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:53
msgid ""
"The uploads folder is shared. To isolate attachments per user, configure "
"host-level directories and access controls."
msgstr ""
"Galka wax lagu shubaa waa la wadaagaa. Si aad u gooni u yeelato lifaaquo "
"kaste user, waxay ku talisaa qaxwooyinka heerka hab-maamulka iyo xakame "
"dadka isticmaala."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:55
msgid ""
"To restore a backup: stop the container, replace the grylli.db file from a "
"backup, and restart."
msgstr ""
"Don dawo da madadin: dakatar da akwati, maye gurbin data/grylli.db da wanda "
"ke daga manyan fayilolin madadin, sannan kuma sake kunna akwatin."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:56
msgid ""
"Admins cannot remove their own admin role to prevent accidental lockout."
msgstr ""
"Maamuleyaasha ma tirtiri karaan jagadaada maamul si looga hortago "
"go'doominta lama filaanka ah."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:58
msgid ""
"Rate limits and automatic account lockouts are enforced to protect against "
"brute-force login attempts."
msgstr ""
"Xadka heerka iyo xayiraadaha xisaabta otomaatigga ah ayaa lagu soo rogayaa "
"si looga ilaaliyo isku-dayga galaangal xoog ku galid."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:60
